author: jonl
msg: Added some parameter validation and finalized some methods that should
not be overridden.  In particular, Component.getSession() is now final
as well as Component.getId().  The change to Component.getId() also
eliminated a field in Page that is really not necessary.  The result of
these changes is a tighter API.  There will be more changes of this
nature as we lock down the API for 1.0 final.
